                    <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:2;23:24" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/xref.dita">The following code sample shows a cross reference to another topic; link text
                         is not provided. Processor typically use the topic title as the link
                         text.</p><codeblock class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xml:space="preserve" xtrc="codeblock:1;25:46" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/xref.dita">&lt;p&gt;Background information about DITA is provided in
&lt;xref href="overview-of-dita.dita"/&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</codeblock><p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:3;26:69" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/xref.dita">The
