<xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:2;28:9" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/xref.dita">href</xmlatt>; using <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:3;28:38" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/xref.dita">keyref</xmlatt> allows the link to be redirected to different
resources when the topic is used in different contexts.</p>
</fig>
